DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

91-854. Cleveland Bar Assn. v. Jurek.

It is ordered by the court, sua sponte, effective August 10, 1995, that Frederick K. Jurek, Attorney Registration No. 0023791, last known address in Cleveland, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s orders of December 31, 1991 and August 15, 1994, to wit: failure to pay board costs in full, including any accrued interest.
